data.title: Science Fiction
data.meta_description: Allbooks En - Free ebook download as Text File (.txt), PDF File (.pdf) or read book online for free. The document lists over 200 anthologies of fiction organized by genre such as science fiction, fantasy, mystery, detective stories, and horror. The anthologies cover various topics like ancient myths and legends, stories inspired by Jane Austen, detective stories set in different cities, supernatural and paranormal romance, and shared universe fiction set in worlds like Dragonlance and Warhammer 40K. The file format and language of each anthology is also provided.
